The whole body is
swathed with wide
vines that are similar to sea

The vines that

body are always jiggling. They
effectively un
nerve its foes.

It tangles any
moving thing with
its vines. Their subtle shaking
is ticklish if you
get ensnared.

During battle, it
constantly moves
the vines that cover its body in
order to annoy its
opponent.

are grabbed. This happens without pain,
allowing it to make a quick getaway. The lost vines are replaced by newly
grown vines the very next day.

Les lianes de Saquedeneu se brisent facilement lorsquon

Wenn man Tangelas Ranken berhrt, fallen diese sofort ab.
Das tut ihm aber nicht weh und es kann sich schnell in
Sicherheit bringen. Verliert es Ranken, werden diese am
nchsten Tag durch neue ersetzt.

A Tangela se le desprenden los tentculos con facilidad en

le crecen otros.

Se afferrate, le liane di Tangela si staccano con facilit,
ma in modo indolore, consentendo cos una pratica
scappatoia. Le liane cadute vengono sostituite da quelle
nuove il giorno dopo.
